==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stylist
<hw>Styl"ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is a master or a model of
style, especially in writing or speaking; a critic of style.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Distinguished as a <qex>stylist</qex>, for ease.</q>
<rj><qau>Fitzed. Hall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stylistic</ent>⟦br⟧
